# WHO ARE WE?

Blue Brain Games is an enthusiastic indie team of graphic artists and developers, all of whom are fans of both 3D puzzle games and the Renaissance genius, Leonardo da Vinci. The House of Da Vinci was successfully funded on Kickstarter in late 2016. After three more successful installments, we are back again to offer you a glimpse of Renaissance Italy from a completely new point of view: yours.
